project: Use "Space" and "Arrow Down" key at the same time to jump down
Use "Arrow Up" key to jump up
Use "Arrow Up" key two time to double jump
Use "f" key to interact/open the chest
Gather the required items to go to the next level
Fun Facts: Your rocks reset when you respawn
Alternatively, You can use "awsd" control instead of arrow
